### Hadith 1:528

*Narrated Abu Al-Mahh:*

We were with Buraida in a battle on a cloudy day and he said, "Offer the
'Asr prayer early as the Prophet said, "Whoever leaves the 'Asr prayer,
all his (good) deeds will be annulled."

